## Frontmatter example

```markdown
---
title: "Example title"
description: "A short description for meta tags and cards."
date: 2026-01-15
tags: ["tag-one", "tag-two"]
lang: en
translationKey: "my-unique-key"
draft: false
---

Content body starts here...
```

## i18n strategy

- Each translatable content type has locale subfolders: `en/`, `it/`, etc.
- Files use the same slug across locales, identified by `translationKey`.
- The `lang` field is the canonical locale identifier — never parse the path.
- `draft: true` entries are excluded from `getStaticPaths()` in production.
